Omnibiologist*
The Omnibiologist is a Biologist, Exobiologist, Chronobiologist,
Xenobiologist and Exoplanar-Biologist all rolled into one.  He is a
complete master of both Botany and Zoology.  He can instantly recognize any
lifeform from any time-period, or from any other planet, or even from any
other plane of existence.  Upon viewing any scroll, he can recite from
memory the complete statistics for that creature.
